snippet.title: Supergirl | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Look out. #Supergirl lands in theaters June 26.

‚ÄúSupergirl,‚Äù DC Studios‚Äô newest feature film to hit the big screen, will be in theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures, starring Milly Alcock in the dual role of Supergirl/Kara Zor-El.  Craig Gillespie directs the film from a screenplay by Ana Nogueira.

snippet.title: Anuv Jain - INAAM (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
The 15th studio recorded single, written, sung and composed by #AnuvJain is here!

Listen to 'Inaam' on all streaming platforms : https://UMGI.lnk.to/Inaam_AnuvJain

For inquiries - anuvjain.work@gmail.com
Instagram - @anuvjain
Manager- aayushman@representmgmt.in

Audio Credits: 

Artist: Anuv Jain (@anuvjain)
Composer: Anuv Jain (@anuvjain)
Producer: Lost Stories (@loststories)
Guitars: Keba Jeremiah (@kebajr)
Choirs: Solomon Konwar (@eskay______) Prachi Kapil (@prachi.kapil8)
Mix Engineers: Rishab Joshi (@rishabjoshi) & Mukul Jain (@mixbymukul)
Master Engineer: Mukul Jain (@mixbymukul)
Recording Engineer: Jay Rana (@itsjayrana)
Additional Programming: Sarthak Kalyani (@sarthak.kalyani)
Dolby Atmos Mastered at Ferris Wheel Studios (@ferriswheelstudios)

Video Credits: 

Director: Bhagyesh Rajeshirke (@bhagyesh_rajeshirke)
Associate Director: Manthan Sharma (@manthan.mp4)
Creative Director: Pranjal Asha (@pranjalasha)
Editor: Manthan Sharma (@manthan.mp4)
Producer: Arnab Kar (@arnab_kar)

Management: REPRESENT
Managers: Shirsodhi Banerjee (@shirsodhi), Kartik Iyer (@kartik_iyer_)

Inaam Lyrics: 

Paragraph 1

Malum 
Hai na 
Hum janay 
Tumko tumse zyada

Tumko 
Mila hai woh
Saalon se 
Jo bhi hai manga

Pre-chorus 1

Kaise khilono ki 
Ro ro ke
Karte the mangay 

Ik bar mil jaye 
Do din mein
Hi bhul jatay  

Chorus 1

Lekin khilono ke dil 
Toh hote hi nahin the

Dil toh humara hai 
Janay galat kya sahi yeh

Kitna the chahte par
Ab tumko yaad na aatey 
Hum

Paragraph 2

Kya yaad tumko 
Tum humko
‚ÄòInaam‚Äô the kehte 

Karte the kitna kuch
Panay ki chah 
Mein pehlay 


Pre-chorus 2

Ab yeh inaam ka 
Tum pe ilzaam hai jana

Dil hai gawah
Jeete jabse ho
Tumko hai hara 

Chorus 2

Cheezein badalti hain 
Itna toh hum ne bhi mana

Itna badal jaogay 
Jana kisne tha jana  

Jo tha parvana 
Ab usko humari parwah na 
Kyun?

Pre-Bridge

Dil mein baat kya hai?
Haan bolo humse 

Chahta aur kya hai? 
Haan bolo humse

Kya kami yahan hai?
Haan bolo humse na

Jo kaha mila hai
Haan bolo humse 

Badle mein bhala hai
Haan bolo humse

Manga tumse kya hai
Hai manga zara sa hi, kya hi, 

Kya? haye

Bas 

Bridge

Jo khat likhe the tumne 
Unhe padh bhi lo zara 
Waadein kiye the jo bhi
Nibhao na aise kabhi

In waadon ki siyahi 
Abhi sukhi hi kahan?
Hai tumhari hi likhai
Yaan bhule ho ye bhi?

Paragraph 3

Kehne ko 
Wah wah 
Tum phir se 
Inaam ho jeete 

Chehre par
Muskan 
Par ankhein hain
Khush na kahin se 

Pre-chorus 3

Humne kaha tha
Hum janey tumko 
Tumse zyada 

Shayad galat the 
Par itna toh 
Humne hai jana 

Chorus 3

Har woh inaam 
Qadar ke bina hi hai waise 

Ghar mein padhe, 
Dhul khate khilono ke jaise

Pal bhar behlaye 
Par dil ko yeh khush na kar paye 
Yoon

Hidden verse

Ghar bethe likhta tha 
Dil ki kahani meri 

Charon taraf thi deewarein 
Deewaron se hi 

Kehta tha ik din 
Jahaan hoga haathon mein hi

Aa aa

Jo tha gumnamo mein 
Ab woh inaamon pe bhi 

Qaidi hai, Qaid hi hai 
Phir bhi dewaron mein hi 

Namumkin khwabon mein
Na khush udane meri 

Aa aa

Bas 

Bridge

Jo khat likhe the tumne 
Unhe padh bhi lo zara 
Waadein kiye the jo bhi
Nibhao na aise kabhi

In waadon ki siyahi 
Abhi sukhi hi kahan?
Hai tumhari hi likhai
Yaan bhule ho ye bhi?

Paragraph 3

Kehne ko 
Wah wah 
Tum phir se 
Inaam ho jeete 

Chehre par
Muskan 
Par ankhein hain
Khush na kahin se 

Pre-chorus 3

Humne kaha tha
Hum janey tumko 
Tumse zyada 

Shayad galat the 
Par itna toh 
Humne hai jana 

Chorus 3

Har woh inaam 
Qadar ke bina hi hai waise 

Ghar mein padhe, 
Dhul khate khilono ke jaise

Pal bhar behlaye 
Par dil ko yeh khush na kar paye 
Yoon

Hidden verse

Ghar bethe likhta tha 
Dil ki kahani meri 

Charon taraf thi deewarein 
Deewaron se hi 

Kehta tha ik din 
Jahaan hoga haathon mein hi

Aa aa

Jo tha gumnamo mein 
Ab woh inaamon pe bhi 

Qaidi hai, Qaid hi hai 
Phir bhi dewaron mein hi 

Namumkin khwabon mein
Na khush udane meri 

Aa aa

snippet.description:
‚ÄúMadi Male Jatra Firav‚Äù is a refined audio-visual presentation that blends authentic Ahirani emotion with traditional Khandeshi cultural expressions. Designed with a cinematic narrative approach, the project showcases the evolving identity of Khandeshi music through world-class production techniques, precise visual storytelling, and polished sound design.

This film-style music video reflects a new direction in regional artistry, elevating local culture with an international visual and audio standard.

Follow the official Instagram for project updates:
https://www.instagram.com/dashuuuuuu___

Hit Music Global Presenting the Ist track from the  "EP" KE HAAL‚Äì ‚ÄúTakiya‚Äù! Sung by Gold E Gill . Lyrics by Sinta. The video is Directed by MP Sega. A film by Sega Production.



Song Credits:
Title: Takiya 
Starring - Sinta Bhai & Seeraj Bajwa
Singer: Gold E Gill 
Lyrics: Sinta Bhai
Music : Gold E Gill
Mix Master: BPM Singh
Guitar : Rajan
Voilan : Manas
Keys Arrangement : Sardana
Hair Stylist: Neeraj

lal jode m thi lyani sare jode tod gi 
mere diye guthi challe jandi jandi mod gi 
nyu dil tod gi ib ram hi bchawega 
kitna m rou mera takiya btawega

aankh ble laal maa puche k hogya re 
roti kyu na khata beta bhukha kyate sogya re
Kyukar batau maa ne kahani k hogi ya
sinte ne krke pagal ghni syani hogi wa 
Je sune meri peed koi sun hi na paawega
kitna m rou mera takiya btawega

kde m rou kde m hansu pdu purani chat teri
tu to soti hogi chain t ro ke kte s rait meri 
dekhe jau pdya phn m kde to call kregi tu 
late thaunga phn tera balka ki dhal fer ldegi tu

dhokha laage kai b tera ibbe msg aawega
kitna m rou mera takiya batawega....
